# File: grunt backup/vendor.css.ab
# Purpose: Backup copy of the vendor CSS bundle from an earlier Grunt build snapshot
# Dependencies: [vendor.css.ab]

## Overview
A preserved copy of a vendor.css build artifact stored in the `grunt backup/` directory. Similar content to `build files - backup/vendor.css` and the root `vendor.css` — concatenated minified third-party CSS (select2, slick-carousel, growl, etc.). Approximately 100 KB, slightly larger than the `build files - backup/` copy, suggesting a different build iteration.

## Interface
No exports. A reference/archive file not loaded by the running application.

## Dependencies
- vendor.css.ab — the canonical source this was copied from

## Implementation Notes
- File size: ~100 KB
- Part of the `grunt backup/` directory, which appears to be a manually created snapshot of a Grunt build output at a different point in time than `build files - backup/`
- Not referenced by any active build configuration or `app/index.html`
